<i>♪ Thunderhead then was
the king of the mountain</i>

7
00:00:37,329 --> 00:00:40,864
<i>♪ Where he lived, nobody knew where</i>

8
00:00:40,958 --> 00:00:44,492
<i>♪ He would steal to the ranches
