for some supper, I suppose?

244
00:16:55,057 --> 00:16:58,058
- Yes, sir.
- Well, why didn't you say so?

245
00:16:58,143 --> 00:17:01,393
Here's five bucks. Have a good time.

246
00:17:01,480 --> 00:17:03,556
Well, thanks.

247
00:17:29,842 --> 00:17:32,759
