Greenway, those Johnny-come-latelies.

277
00:19:53,110 --> 00:19:55,435
You stay away from those McLaughlins.

278
00:19:55,529 --> 00:19:57,771
Go down and have your supper.

279
00:19:57,865 --> 00:20:00,272
You heard me, now.

280
00:20:09,126 --> 00:20:11,284
